---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms of Use | Junction Retro">
  <main class="bg-[#F5F5F0] min-h-screen py-24 px-8 md:px-16 selection:bg-indigo-100 selection:text-indigo-900 font-sans">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      
      <a href="/" class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-slate-400 hover:text-slate-900 transition-colors mb-16 inline-block">
        ← Back to Site
      </a>

      <header class="mb-20 border-b border-slate-200 pb-12">
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-serif text-slate-900 mb-6 tracking-tighter">
          Terms of Use
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.5em] text-indigo-600 font-bold">
          Archive Access Protocol v.2026
        </p>
      </header>

      <article class="prose prose-slate prose-lg text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
        
        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-slate-900 mb-4 uppercase tracking-tight">1. Intellectual Property</h2>
          <p>
            All content hosted within the Junction Retro archive—including high-resolution photography, technical descriptions, and curated dossiers—is the exclusive property of <strong>Junction Retro</strong>. Unauthorized reproduction, scraping, or commercial use of our archival imagery is strictly prohibited.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-slate-900 mb-4 uppercase tracking-tight">2. Accuracy of Information</h2>
          <p>
            While we strive for historical and mechanical precision, vehicle descriptions are provided for informational purposes. Final verification of vehicle specifications and provenance is the responsibility of the potential acquirer during the inspection process.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-slate-900 mb-4 uppercase tracking-tight">3. Limitation of Liability</h2>
          <p>
            Junction Retro shall not be held liable for any digital disruptions or inaccuracies within the archive. We reserve the right to modify or withdraw any vehicle dossier without prior notice.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-12">
          <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-slate-900 mb-4 uppercase tracking-tight">4. Governing Law</h2>
          <p>
            These terms are governed by the laws of <strong>Belgium</strong>. Any disputes arising from the use of this digital archive shall be settled within the jurisdiction of the courts of Liege.
          </p>
        </section>
      </article>

    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>